@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to SmartAdopt, your trusted online pet shop. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data when you visit our website or use our services. By accessing or using SmartAdopt, you agree to the practices described in this policy.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
            We may collect the following types of information:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and home address when you register, place an order, or contact us.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit card details or other payment methods, processed securely through third-party providers.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you interact with our website, such as IP address, browser type, and pages visited, collected via cookies and tracking technologies.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Pet Information:</strong> Details about your pets (e.g., breed, age) when you adopt or seek advice from our services.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>
            We use your data to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">Process and fulfill your pet adoption or purchase orders.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Improve our website and services based on your preferences and feedback.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Send you promotional offers, newsletters, or updates (with your consent).</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Ensure the security and functionality of our platform.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Comply with legal obligations, such as tax or regulatory requirements.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
        <p>
            We do not sell your personal information. We may share it with:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">Service providers (e.g., payment processors, email services) to operate our business.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Legal authorities if required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Business partners with your explicit consent for joint promotions.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
            We implement industry-standard security measures, including encryption and secure servers, to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no online system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">6. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p>
            You have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">Access, update, or delete your personal information by contacting us at privacy@smartadopt.com.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Opt out of marketing emails by clicking the unsubscribe link in any email.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Request data portability or restrict processing under applicable laws.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            To exercise these rights, please email us at the address above. We will respond within 30 days.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
            We use cookies to enhance your experience and analyze website usage. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings, though disabling them may limit some features.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">8. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p>
            SmartAdopt is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from minors. If we learn of such collection, we will delete it promptly.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted here with an updated date. Continued use of our site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new policy.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            For questions or concerns, please reach out to us at:
            <br />
            Email: privacy@smartadopt.com
            <br />
            Address: 123 Pet Lane, Bucharest, Romania
        </p>
    </section>
</div>